  - key: Card_Shovel_Des
    kor: "<#fbc531> \u25A0</color> 100% \uD30C\uAD34"
    eng: Destroys tiles in the yellow attack range with 100% chance.\\n(Tool) This
      card may be destroyed upon use.\\nUpgrading this card removes the destruction
      effect.
  - key: Card_Rake_Des
    kor: "<#fbc531> \u25A0</color> 100% \uD30C\uAD34<br><#efefe9> \u25A0</color>
      66% \uD30C\uAD34"
    eng: Destroys tiles in the yellow attack range with 100% chance.\\nDestroys tiles
      in the white attack range with 66% chance.\\n(Tool) This card may be destroyed
      upon use.\\nUpgrading this card removes the destruction effect.
  - key: Card_Shovel_Enhanced_Des
    kor: "<#fbc531> \u25A0</color> 100% \uD30C\uAD34"
    eng: Destroys tiles in the yellow attack range with 100% chance.\\n(Enhanced)
      Destroys tiles ignoring obstacle blocks.
  - key: Card_Rake_Enhanced_Des
    kor: "<#fbc531> \u25A0</color><#efefe9> \u25A0</color> 100% \uD30C\uAD34"
    eng: Destroys tiles in both yellow and white attack ranges with 100% chance.
