    eng: Destroys tiles in the yellow attack range with 100% chance.\\nTiles in the
      white attack range cannot be destroyed.\\nIf 3 or more tiles are destroyed
      with this card, all normal tiles in the attack range are destroyed.\\nGrants
      2 Gold for each Cracked tile destroyed.\\nIf 5 tiles are destroyed with this
      card, draw 1 Golden-tag card from your deck.\\n(Tool) This card may be destroyed
      upon use.\\nUpgrading this card removes the destruction effect.
